Your Honor,

I stand before this court today to accept full responsibility for my actions. I plead guilty to the charge of being drunk and disorderly. I understand the seriousness of my offense and I am deeply remorseful for the way I conducted myself on that day.

I acknowledge that my behavior was unacceptable and that I should have exercised better control over my actions. It was a day where I simply wanted to prioritize myself and let go of all the outside pressures I was facing. However, I now realize that my actions were inappropriate and caused disturbance to those around me.

